snippet: When Geoff Ogilvy’s drop in the rankings kept him out of tournaments, he saw it as a “wake-up call.” At the Honda Classic, he is tied for third after three rounds.
abstract: Luke Guthrie and Michael Thompson share third-round lead at Honda Classic golf tournament; Geoff Ogilvy, who is tied for third, scrambles his way into contention.
lead_paragraph: When Geoff Ogilvy’s drop in the rankings kept him out of tournaments, he saw it as a “wake-up call.” At the Honda Classic, he is tied for third after three rounds.

headline.seo: Geoff Ogilvy Climbs Into Contention at Honda Classic
headline.main: After Slump, Ogilvy Climbs Into Contention
headline.print_headline: After Slump, Ogilvy Climbs Into Contention
